  • By default url will load from the topology file

  • XIQSE Load Page and Log In   ${USERNAME}   ${PASSWORD}   ${URL}   incognito_mode=True

Parameters

  • username – login account username

  • password – login account password

  • url – url to load

  • incognito_mode – indicates whether or not to open the browser in incognito/private mode

Returns

1 if login successful else -1
